    Movie
    Represents a movie Each movie is associated to one or many movie reviews.
    MovieGoer
    Represents a movie goer
    MovieReview
    Represents a movie review
    MovieScreening
    Represents a movie screening Each movie screening is associated with one movie and cinema
    MovieTicket
    Represents a movie ticket Each movie screening is associated with one movie screening and seat
    PlatinumCinema
